	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">Dum haec scripsi, mi <persName ref="p495">Bullingere</persName>, quatriduo hęseram in lectulo et corpusculum iam agens annum sexagesimum quintum vix e grabbattulo erexeram et cogor scribere.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Quare obsecro, si quid erratum, tu melius interpretare.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Hoc oro: Sufficit mihi; tolle, quęso, animam meam.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Fiat domini voluntas.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la">Praestantissimo viro domino <persName ref="p495">Henrycho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587">Tigurino</placeName> theologo, suo domino observando etc.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="de">Zürch.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Darunter von <persName ref="p495">Bullingers</persName> Hand:]</note>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="de"><placeName>Rychenwyler</placeName> enderung.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
